review: Room was dirty, with marker scribbles on the walls.

room_title: Escape room "Return from Wonderland" by Room Escape Williamsburg in Williamsburg
review: You can tell that the rooms were well thought out and imaginative. We loved the "Alice in Wonderland" room. Great fun for the whole family!

room_title: Escape room "Return from Wonderland" by Room Escape Williamsburg in Williamsburg
review: Had a great time with the Wonderland room. Not knowing if clues are literal or not is half the fun. We managed to get thru and truly enjoyed it. Would definitely try the other rooms!!!
